            <p class="text-justify">Air New Zealand is an airline based in Auckland, New Zealand, founded in 1940 as Tasman Empire Airways Limited (TEAL). The airline operates its services to20 domestic and 32 international destinations in 18 countries, primarily around and within the Pacific Rim with a fleet size of 103 aircraft. Air New Zealand is known for its frequent flyer program called Airpoints and lounges with valet parking, priority wait listing, exclusive check-in, extra checked in baggage and preferred seating. </p>
